summary:
So uhh...
Parts of Detective Pikachu were filmed in London. Sword and Shield will feature the Pokémon world equivalent to...
body:
So uhh…

Parts of Detective Pikachu were filmed in London. Sword and Shield will feature the Pokémon world equivalent to London.

Ryme City is a big modern metropolis, just like the city that’s standing in London’s place on the Galar region map.

Detective Pikachu features Pokémon from all regions. Before Sword and Shield were revealed, the devs implied in an interview that they were working on a game where you can truly “catch ‘em all”.

The main character of Detective Pikachu arrives in Ryme City by train. There’s a train system that travels between the cities of the Galar region, including its version of London.

Basically I’m saying it’s possible that Detective Pikachu takes place in Galar.
